NG","body":"虽然记不清是几岁的事了，\n但我偶尔会在家附近的公园看到一群\n关系很好的女孩子","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf05","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event280-05-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"现在想想，那多半就是\nAfterglow的大家","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event280-05-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"但我从幼儿园开始就在白雪学园上学，\n所以没和她们一起玩过","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event280-05-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"LAYER","body":"是这样啊……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event280-05-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"一想到现在通过乐队和打工和她们变成了好朋友，\n就觉得这是一种很奇妙的缘分呢","tenti